Package org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.api.crafting

Class CraftingJobDependencyGraph

java.lang.Object
org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.api.crafting.CraftingJobDependencyGraph
public class CraftingJobDependencyGraph extends Object
A CraftingJobDependencyGraph stores dependencies between crafting jobs based on their unique ID.

    • mergeCraftingJobs

      public void mergeCraftingJobs(CraftingJob target, CraftingJob mergee, boolean markMergeeAsFinished)
      Merge the two crafting jobs by adding the second job's amount into the first job's amount. Furthermore, all dependencies of the second job will be merged into the dependencies of the first job as well.
      Parameters:
      target - The job that should be merged into.
      mergee - The job that should be removed and merged into the target job.
      markMergeeAsFinished - If the mergee job should be marked as finished.
